OL,5, Labour is calling for a parliamentary  
OL,6, investigation into claims the chairman 
OL,7, of the BBC helped Boris Johnson secure 
OL,8, a loan - weeks before the then-prime   
OL,9, minister recommended him for the role. 
OL,11,FThe Sunday Times says Richard Sharp was
OL,12,Finvolved in arranging a guarantor on a 
OL,13,Floan of up to #800,000 for Mr Johnson. 
OL,15,FMr Sharp said he had "simply connected"
OL,16,Fpeople and there was no conflict of    
OL,17,Finterest.                              
OL,19,FMr Johnson's spokesman said he did not 
OL,20,Freceive financial advice from Mr Sharp.
